### ===========================================
### SIMPLE FRIEND API TESTS
### ===========================================

### 1. Send friend request (User 1 -> User 2)
POST http://localhost:8080/friends/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": 1,
  "receiver_id": 2
}

### 2. Check friends of user 1
GET http://localhost:8080/friends/1

### 3. Check friends of user 2
GET http://localhost:8080/friends/2

### 4. Accept friend request (User 2 accepts from User 1)
PUT http://localhost:8080/friends/accept
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": 1,
  "receiver_id": 2
}

### 5. Check friends again after accepting
GET http://localhost:8080/friends/1

### 6. Check friends again after accepting
GET http://localhost:8080/friends/2

### 7. Block friend (User 1 blocks User 2)
PUT http://localhost:8080/friends/block
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": 1,
  "receiver_id": 2
}

### 8. Unfriend (User 1 unfriends User 2)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/friends/unfriend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender_id": 1,
  "receiver_id": 2
}